---
import Container from "./Container.astro";
---

<div id="integration" class="py-24">
  <Container>
    <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:items-start">
      <section class="space-y-6">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-primary">Integrating people, process, and technology</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white md:text-4xl">
          Connect strategy, execution, and AI in one shared view
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
          We create a shared view of how strategy turns into execution, connecting teams, tools, and governance so AI delivers measurable value.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
          <li>• Map the <strong>WHAT</strong> of your business and the core workflows that power growth.</li>
          <li>• Trace the <strong>CAPABILITIES</strong> and systems that enable those workflows.</li>
          <li>• Make <strong>ACCOUNTABILITY</strong> explicit across every process.</li>
          <li>• Deliver the right information to the right people at the right time.</li>
          <li>• Surface the <strong>KPIs</strong> that matter to the business strategy.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="space-y-6 rounded-3xl border border-primary/20 p-10 shadow-lg shadow-primary/5 dark:border-primary/40 dark:bg-gray-950">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">How we embed continuity</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-1 size-2 rounded-full bg-primary"></span><span>Stand up a process management system so institutional knowledge is searchable and reusable.</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-1 size-2 rounded-full bg-primary"></span><span>Segment the organisation into business capabilities to focus investment where it matters most.</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-1 size-2 rounded-full bg-primary"></span><span>Institute process governance that enforces standardisation, ownership, and communication.</span></li>
          <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="mt-1 size-2 rounded-full bg-primary"></span><span>Create aligned visibility through process QBRs and steering committees that keep change on track.</span></li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>
  </Container>
</div>
